    "summary": "The user expresses a paranoid/delusional belief that birds are using a sophisticated, intentional \"tactical language\" to coordinate weather-related movements. The assistant consistently reframes these observations through a scientific, instinctual lens, explaining the behaviors as evolved biological responses rather than conscious communication.",
